Package spring.service

Class UserService

  • java.lang.Object
    • spring.service.UserService
  • @Service
public class UserService
extends java.lang.Object
    Service for handling all requests related to Users. Maintains a proxy of Users for each session.
    Author:
    Shane Lockwood

      • loadByPage

        public Proxy<User> loadByPage​(java.lang.String sessionId,
                              java.lang.String keyword,
                              int page)
        Loads Users from a database with usernames that contain the passed keyword. Proxies the returne Users with the passed page and returns the Proxy. The proxied data is sorted with UserComparatorByVote.
        Parameters:
        sessionId - The String representing the session's id.
        keyword - The String to be used in the database query.
        page - The int representing the subset of data to be stored in the Proxy.
        Returns:
        Proxy
